---
---
<section id="presse" class="py-16 sm:py-24 px-5 sm:px-8 bg-brand-warm relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.03] pointer-events-none"
       style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle, #1a3a5c 1.5px, transparent 1.5px); background-size: 28px 28px;"></div>

  <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-10 sm:mb-12">
      <p class="text-brand-gold font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs mb-3">Ils parlent de nous</p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl text-brand-blue font-bold">Passerelles dans la presse</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-5 sm:gap-6">

      <a href="/images/article-dna.jpg" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
         class="group bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm border border-stone-200 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-brand-gold hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col">
        <div class="relative overflow-hidden" style="padding-top: 52%;">
          <img src="/images/article-dna.jpg"
               alt="Article DNA avril 2024"
               class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover object-top group-hover:scale-[1.03] transition-transform duration-500"/>
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/50 via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
          <span class="absolute top-3 left-3 text-white text-xs font-semibold bg-brand-blue px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full shadow">DNA · Avril 2024</span>
        </div>
        <div class="p-5 sm:p-6 flex-1 flex flex-col">
          <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2 text-base sm:text-lg leading-snug">
            Des diplômes pour des élèves venus d'ailleurs
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed flex-1">
            Les apprenants à l'honneur pour leur persévérance dans l'apprentissage du français — Dernières Nouvelles d'Alsace.
          </p>
          <p class="text-brand-gold text-xs font-semibold mt-3 group-hover:underline">Voir l'article →</p>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="/images/article-2026.jpg" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
         class="group bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm border border-stone-200 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-brand-gold hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col">
        <div class="relative overflow-hidden" style="padding-top: 52%;">
          <img src="/images/article-2026.jpg"
               alt="Bulletin municipal Neuf-Brisach Info 2026"
               class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover object-top group-hover:scale-[1.03] transition-transform duration-500"/>
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/50 via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
          <span class="absolute top-3 left-3 text-white text-xs font-semibold bg-brand-blue px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full shadow">Neuf-Brisach Info · 2026</span>
        </div>
        <div class="p-5 sm:p-6 flex-1 flex flex-col">
          <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2 text-base sm:text-lg leading-snug">
            Passerelles dans le bulletin municipal
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed flex-1">
            Bénévoles, formatrices et apprenants à l'honneur dans le bulletin de Neuf-Brisach.
          </p>
          <p class="text-brand-gold text-xs font-semibold mt-3 group-hover:underline">Voir l'article →</p>
        </div>
      </a>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
